KashiKartCiCd Deployment Guide (AWS EC2 + Aurora + Local Frontend)
1️⃣ Prerequisites

On AWS EC2 (Ubuntu 22.04, t3.micro or similar):

Python 3.10+
PostgreSQL/Aurora RDS
Node.js & npm (if building frontend on server)
Git
pip packages in a virtual environment

On Local Mac:

Node.js & npm
Git
Access to AWS EC2 (via key pair)
Frontend code
